Quickstrike:





Quickstrike sighed, with his back against the wall, looking left and right. 
He put his foot up against the metal wall, and chuckled softly to himself. 
No pain. He loved it.

He soon gave up on waiting on Megatron. He wasn't a bot with much patience. 
If he hadn't anything to do to occupy himself he'd become twitchy or get 
himself in trouble.

He walked through the halls, then though maybe he should pay Rattrap a 
little visit.

He grinned.
